    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a great car for me. It\u2019s in solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014definitely ready for its next adventure! I've taken really good care of it, and it definitely shows. If you're looking for something reliable that still looks great on the road, this is the one. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 29900.0,
