    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Silver Grey Metallic. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to reach an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension has been sharpened with polyurethane bushings and adjustable dampers for improved turn-in and lateral stability. While showing minor cosmetic wear commensurate with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, following a recent valve clearance adjustment. A visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
