    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it's officially ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has been a total joy to drive. If you\u2019re looking for a solid, reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. I've taken good care of it, and it's got plenty of life left to give. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 29500.0,
